This paper deals with the problem of semantic segmentation in medical pathological images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. The proposed method involves the use of attention mechanisms, which are also commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. Additionally, the paper involves the analysis of whole slide images, which is a topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) research.
